          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 11,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Beidou_icon.png",
                      "name": "北斗",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "北斗在「魔王武裝」組隊中是一位比較重要的角色，她能夠在後臺利用元素爆發的雷元素傷害穩定觸發感電反應（值得注意的是，感電傷害不受該武器特效加成），感電反應下水雷可以共存，因此北斗元素爆發傷害在「魔王武裝」組隊中一般都能享受武器特效加成，對「魔王武裝」組隊裡的北斗而言是不錯的選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 21,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Sayu_icon.png",
                      "name": "早柚",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "當早柚命座比較高時，該武器提供的高額",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "則可以直接加成早柚的治療量和元素充能效率。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
